Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: Community <your_email@example.com>
Depends: dkms, build-essential, kmod, systemd, libc6
Description: Community ARM64 wrapper/package builder for Synology Active Backup for Business Agent via Box64
 Runs Synology ABB x86_64 Linux agent on ARM64 using Box64 and native ARM64 synosnap DKMS module.
 This package is unofficial and unsupported by Synology.

